ingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-8-190x127.jpg 190w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-8-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-8-16x11.jpg 16w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-8.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1340px) 100vw, 1340px\" /><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">As expected, Alaphilippe made his move on the Poggio &#8230;</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1340\" height=\"893\" src=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6-1340x893.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"504890\" data-full-url=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6.jpg\" data-link=\"https://cyclingtips.com/?attachment_id=504890\" class=\"wp-image-504890\" srcset=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6-1340x893.jpg 1340w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6-650x433.jpg 650w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6-190x127.jpg 190w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6-16x11.jpg 16w, https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-6.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1340px) 100vw, 1340px\" /><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">&#8230; prompting his rivals to follow as best they could.</figcaption></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1340\" height=\"893\" src=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/2021-milan-sanremo-corvos-2-1340x893.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"504881\" data-full-url=\"https://cyclingtips.com/wp-conte